Act Report¶

Documentation of analysis and insights into final data

Real-world data rarely comes clean. Using Python and its libraries, we will gather data from a variety of sources and in a variety of formats, assess its quality and tidiness, then clean it. This is called data wrangling.

Though there are 5000+ tweets in the dataset, not all are dog ratings and some are retweets, we remove the reweets and focus on orginal tweets.

Project goal¶

Wrangle WeRateDogs Twitter data to create interesting and trustworthy analyses and visualizations.

After gathering, assessing, and cleaning data, we stored it in a new CSV file called: twitter_archive_master.csv

Insight 1: Determine most commonly used Source¶

Through the analysis, it becomes clear to us that WeRateDogs account uses the iPhone very heavily to post Twitter tweets, 2042 of the tweets were written through the iPhone.

  • Vine - Make a Scene: 91
  • Twitter for iPhone: 2042
  • Twitter Web Client: 31
  • TweetDeck: 11

Insight 2: Mean Retweet and Mean Favorite of 'WeRateDogs' account¶

This relationship shows the effect of retweets on increasing the rate of tweet favorites. When you retweet the tweet, the viewership of the tweet increases, and therefore there is a greater possibility of increasing the number of favorites. The graph shows an increase in the number of retweets and favorites through time and the favorites much higher increases than retweets.

Insight 3: Time series analysis of Twitter data¶

The WeRateDogs account started posting tweets on Twitter in 2015, and in the same year they achieved the highest number of tweets in their account, then this percentage gradually decreased until it stopped in 2017. Therefore, we can investigate that the number of tweets is decreased over time. The highest number of tweets were posted by WeRateDogs account is in 2015-12 (November 2015), which Published 388 tweets.

Insight 4: Most common dog stage and Breeds¶

From the graphs we can see that the most commonly dog stage is PUPPER and the most commonly type is GOLDEN_RETRIEVER. Therefore most of people prefare to choose PUPPER dogs than other stages and DOGGO stsge come next.

Insight 5: Most frequently words¶

From the word cloud we can see the most frequently words in the posts like dog stage : pupper, doggo
